        "original": "確かに。お腹空きましたね。",
        "english": "True. I'm hungry.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:36.500",
        "end": "00:38.200",
        "original": "あ、運転手さん、まっすぐね。",
        "english": "Ah, driver, go straight.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
