        "original": "フブちゃんたちがついてきてる。",
        "english": "Fubu-chan and the others are following us.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:45.900",
        "end": "00:49.000",
        "original": "おらおらフブ様寂しくなっちゃったのかね。",
        "english": "My, my, did Fubu-sama get lonely?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
